| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-4384 — Recovery Inhibition (sinobi)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 94f6152f-e8a6-5ecc-8d3c-9d725f678df3"
